      <hedline>
        <hl1>Introduction</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Sampling of reader responses to articles on new TV technology and culture clash between Jews in Beachwood, Ohio (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Our article on the new TV technology like TiVo and Replay uncovered surprising support for the old: many readers said the ''impossible'' VCR gets a bad rap. And the report on a culture clash between Jews in Beachwood, Ohio, prompted others to ask, What would Joe Lieberman do?</p>
      </block>
